'''HeForShe'''(又常被稱作 '''He for She'''，中文譯作「他為她」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5081420|title=艾瑪華森　多了妳，世界才會不一樣|date=2017-03-15|newspaper=天下雜誌618期《姊無所畏》p.66|accessdate=2017-03-15|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317032549/http://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5081420|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「他为了她」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cn.unhabitat.org/executive-direorshe-campaign/|title=联合国人居署执行主任在“他为了她”活动中签字|accessdate=2015-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813230536/https://cn.unhabitat.org/executive-direorshe-campaign/|archive-date=2017-08-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hku.hk/press/press-releases/detail/c_12579.html|title=港大全球首間大學在校園啟動「他為了她」|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012011123/http://www.hku.hk/press/press-releases/detail/c_12579.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「男性促进女性权利」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=25778|title=妇女署以全球丰富多彩的活动庆祝2016“国际妇女节”|accessdate=2016-03-17|work=联合国新闻|archive-date=2017-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814021223/http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=25778|dead-url=no}}</ref>) 是一個由[[联合国妇女权能署|聯合國婦女權能署]]發起以促進[[性別平等|性別平等]]為宗旨的團結性活動，該活動鼓勵[[男性|男性]]勇於對日常生活中發生之一切負面性別不平等事件做出行動，並藉此成為改變社會的原動力。 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2014/09/22/emma-watson-recruits-men-to-make-the-world-safer-for-women-with-heforshe-campaign/|title=Emma Watson: Feminism too often is seen as 'man-hating'|accessdate=22 September 2014|author=McDonald, Soraya Nadia|date=22 September 2014|work=Washington Post|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317085159/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2014/09/22/emma-watson-recruits-men-to-make-the-world-safer-for-women-with-heforshe-campaign/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Family/Modern-Parenthood/2014/0922/Emma-Watson-and-HeForShe-Points-to-flaws-in-man-hating|title=Emma Watson and HeForShe: Points to flaws in man-hating|accessdate=22 September 2014|author=Suhay, Lisa|date=22 September 2014|work=The Christian Science Monitor|archive-date=2017-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814023455/https://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Family/Modern-Parenthood/2014/0922/Emma-Watson-and-HeForShe-Points-to-flaws-in-man-hating|dead-url=no}}</ref> 本於性別平等是一個對於全人類各個層面都有影響的議題，該活動尋求男性加入原本被認為僅與[[女性|女性]]相關的運動。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/7966|title=如果你喜歡艾瑪華森的聯合國演講，你也該知道這個關鍵字#HeForShe|date=2014-10-04|newspaper=The News Lens 關鍵評論網|accessdate=2017-03-04|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304044735/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/7966|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/21/P2017022100496.htm|title=勞工及福利局局長出席婦女事務委員會研討會2017全體會議致辭（只有中文）（附圖）|accessdate=2017-03-04|work=www.info.gov.hk|archive-date=2017-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304045351/http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/21/P2017022100496.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Portal box|女性主义}}

